(2763, 269, 'section_2_headline', 'A values-driven company'),
(2764, 269, '_section_2_headline', 'field_5c4b46ff25f41'),
(2765, 269, 'section_2_text', 'The World Class Contracting Mission is to live up to our company name on every project from start to finish. Our goal is to continue our success as a proven leader in the Mechanical Construction Industry, providing our customers with the best value in their Construction projects.\r\nWe train and retain professional people with a strong work ethic, who take pride in their work. Our team continues to build upon our reputation, recognized as a world-class organization with the highest levels of safety, craftsmanship, and integrity'),
(2766, 269, '_section_2_text', 'field_5c4b470d25f42'),
(2767, 269, 'section_3_gallary', ''),
(2768, 269, '_section_3_gallary', 'field_5c4b471a25f43'),
(2769, 269, 'section_4_content_0_headline', 'Honesty and Integrity'),
(2770, 269, '_section_4_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(2771, 269, 'section_4_content_0_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. serves its customers and treats its competitors, subcontractors and suppliers with honesty and integrity. We avoid conflicts of interest, both corporate and individual. Where a corporate conflict exists, World Class Contracting Ltd will disclose such conflict to its customer or prospective customer. World Class Contracting Ltd. regularly educates its staff about personal conflicts of interest and has established a procedure for internal disclosure. World Class Contracting Ltd. does not knowingly violate any law or regulation'),
(2772, 269, '_section_4_content_0_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(2773, 269, 'section_4_content_0_image', '245'),
(2774, 269, '_section_4_content_0_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(2775, 269, 'section_4_content_1_headline', 'Safety'),
(2776, 269, '_section_4_content_1_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(2777, 269, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd assures that the safety of its employees, the employees of others on the job site, and the general public at large, is given the highest priority in all aspects of the firms activities. World Class Contracting Ltd will strive to provide its employees with the proper training and education required to enable the company to meet the stated goals of a safe workplace.'),
(2778, 269, '_section_4_content_1_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(2779, 269, 'section_4_content_1_image', '245'),
(2780, 269, '_section_4_content_1_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(2781, 269, 'section_4_content_2_headline', 'Environmental Accountability'),
(2782, 269, '_section_4_content_2_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(2783, 269, 'section_4_content_2_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. will endeavour to promote sustainable building practices and environmental considerations in all its operations and in the services it provides to its clients. World Class Contracting Ltd will strive to provide its employees with the proper training and education required to enable the company to meet the stated goals of a more sustainable built environment and more environmentally friendly business practices.'),
(2784, 269, '_section_4_content_2_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(2785, 269, 'section_4_content_2_image', '245'),
(2786, 269, '_section_4_content_2_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(2787, 269, 'section_4_content_3_headline', 'Standards of Practice'),
(2788, 269, '_section_4_content_3_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(2789, 269, 'section_4_content_3_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. provides materials and services in a manner consistent with the established and accepted standards of the construction industry and with the laws and regulations that govern it including the use of standard industry documents wherever feasible. The firm performs its contracts with competence, reasonable care and diligence. The firm establishes prices that are commensurate with its services.'),
(2790, 269, '_section_4_content_3_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(2791, 269, 'section_4_content_3_image', '245'),
(2792, 269, '_section_4_content_3_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(2793, 269, 'section_4_content_4_headline', 'Competition'),
(2794, 269, '_section_4_content_4_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(2795, 269, 'section_4_content_4_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. competes fairly for contracts, avoiding any practice that might be construed to be in violation of the letter or spirit of federal or provincial competition or unfair business practices legislation. The firm does not seek nor accept information concerning a competitors bid prior to bid closing nor does it attempt to modify its price after the bid closing. The firm avoids any activity that could be construed as *bid shopping, a **reverse bid auction or ***bid peddling.'),
(2796, 269, '_section_4_content_4_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(2797, 269, 'section_4_content_4_image', '245'),
(2798, 269, '_section_4_content_4_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(2799, 269, 'section_4_content', '5'),
(2800, 269, '_section_4_content', 'field_5c4b473525f44'),
(2801, 269, 'section_5_content_0_headline', 'Health & Safety'),
(2802, 269, '_section_5_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(2803, 269, 'section_5_content_0_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. is committed to working with our employees in order to create working conditions that promote safe, healthy, and efficient operations and to eliminate or control hazards that cause incidents, injuries or damage to the environment. We believe excellence in practice is vital to the wellbeing of all people directly or indirectly involved in our business.\r\n<strong>We maintain a Certificate of Recognition (COR) for our Safety Program.</strong>'),
(2804, 269, '_section_5_content_0_text', 'field_5c4b4b9aabd51'),
