(2807, 269, 'section_5_content_1_headline', 'What is COR?'),
(2808, 269, '_section_5_content_1_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(2809, 269, 'section_5_content_1_text', 'A COR shows that the employers health and safety management system has been evaluated by a certified auditor and meets provincial standards. These standards are established by Occupational Health and Safety (OHS). It aims to reduce the human and financial costs associated with workplace accidents and injuries. The COR certification is the highest distinction available in the industry.'),
