(4502, 326, 'section_5_content_0_headline', 'Health & Safety'),
(4503, 326, '_section_5_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(4504, 326, 'section_5_content_0_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. is committed to working with our employees in order to create working conditions that promote safe, healthy, and efficient operations and to eliminate or control hazards that cause incidents, injuries or damage to the environment. We believe excellence in practice is vital to the wellbeing of all people directly or indirectly involved in our business.\r\n<strong>We maintain a Certificate of Recognition (COR) for our Safety Program.</strong>\r\n\r\n<h3>What is COR?</h3>\r\nA COR shows that the employers health and safety management system has been evaluated by a certified auditor and meets provincial standards. These standards are established by Occupational Health and Safety (OHS). It aims to reduce the human and financial costs associated with workplace accidents and injuries. The COR certification is the highest distinction available in the industry.'),
(4505, 326, '_section_5_content_0_text', 'field_5c4b4b9aabd51'),
(4506, 326, 'section_5_content_0_icon', '290'),
(4507, 326, '_section_5_content_0_icon', 'field_5c4b4ba4abd52'),
(4508, 326, 'section_5_content_1_headline', 'Our Commitment'),
(4509, 326, '_section_5_content_1_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(4510, 326, 'section_5_content_1_text', 'The Management at World Class Contracting Ltd., is committed to maintaining a safe and healthy workplace while protecting the environment. We continuously strive to improve our HSE Performance and prevent injuries and illness by maintaining stringent policies and procedures, meeting or exceeding all applicable laws and regulations.'),
