(4699, 329, '_section_4_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(4700, 329, 'section_4_content_0_text', '<strong>World Class Contracting Ltd.</strong> serves its customers and treats its competitors, subcontractors and suppliers with honesty and integrity. We avoid conflicts of interest, both corporate and individual. Where a corporate conflict exists, World Class Contracting Ltd will disclose such conflict to its customer or prospective customer.\r\n\r\n<strong> World Class Contracting Ltd.</strong> regularly educates its staff about personal conflicts of interest and has established a procedure for internal disclosure. World Class Contracting Ltd. does not knowingly violate any law or regulation'),
