(1140, 155, 'section_2_headline', 'Why World Class Contracting?'),
(1141, 155, '_section_2_headline', 'field_5c4a47eb4bbe3'),
(1142, 155, 'section_2_text', 'World Class Contracting offers experience, innovative ideas and the desire and dedication to provide an exceptional building experience to our customers, all backed by a solid team of highly skilled tradespeople. WCC is committed to seeking innovative solutions, exceeding expectations with quality, timely construction, and safety excellence. \r\n\r\nOur Expertise ranges from designing, installing and retrofitting mechanical systems in Commercial, Greenhouse Growing Facilities, Municipal, Institutional, Education, Sports & Leisure, Multi-family Residential, Estates, and Healthcare facilities. We have the capability of providing and designing 3D drawings which assist in visual planning and enables prefabrication welding for mechanical rooms, which is an advantage to construction schedules.\r\n'),
(1143, 155, '_section_2_text', 'field_5c4a47fc4bbe4'),
(1144, 155, 'section_3_content_0_headline', 'Our History'),
(1145, 155, '_section_3_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4a484e4bbe7'),
(1146, 155, 'section_3_content_0_text', 'The corporation was founded in 1999 out of Dickson Alberta, and then moved on to establish operation headquarters out of Red Deer Alberta in 2005. The company has continued to grow to become one of the most prominent Mechanical Contractors in Central Alberta.'),
