(1152, 155, 'section_3_content_1_text', 'From the initial contact to the close out of a project, our customers can be assured that we are fully engaged in executing their vision. With direction from our solid Project Management Team we are able to manage all aspects of the mechanical installation in a professional and timely manner. \r\n\r\nOur Formula for Success:  PLAN > MATERIAL > MANPOWER\r\n'),
