(3857, 245, '_section_4_content_1_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(3858, 245, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting takes great pride in being a part of the design of a project. Including us in the design process helps to eliminate many design conflicts that can occur structurally, architecturally and between the other trades. This proactive approach in turn helps to save the project time and money early on.\r\n'),
